This is the best ever. Touched by an angel was the best tv show ever. It has good meaning and good values. I would love there to be more shows like them !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

This is an excellent show,with lots of morals and talk about the Lord and the message of how He loves us. I was a little confused by the inclusion of the very last show that was aired, being part of this set. But I must say that I have enjoyed watching my d.v.d.s of this show alot.

The TV series Touched By An Angel is great entertainment for the whole family.  Your never too old or young to be touched by the heart warming stories. My only regret is that this show is no longer on the air.

I was overjoyed with the product but disappointed when my mother contacted me and said the dvd would not play on her player. I have since discovered that they are region 1 DVD's and Australia is region 4. Now my mother has to purchase a compatible machine. I was unaware of this criteria when purchasing overseas products.

Every episode is a delight and leaves me with a warm and fuzzy!  Where are the rest of the season's episodes CBS. There are many who are looking for more, I assure you!  what a great series. Thanks Martha!
